org.rapidcontext.util

Interface HttpUtil

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppWebService, FileWebService, ProcedureWebService, Request, StorageWebService, WebDavRequest, WebService

    public interface HttpUtil
    A set of utility methods and constants for the HTTP protocol.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Per Cederberg

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static interface  HttpUtil.HEADER
      A number of standard HTTP headers as defined in RFC1945 (HTTP/1.0), RFC2616 (HTTP/1.1), and RFC4918 (WebDAV).
      static class  HttpUtil.Helper
      Some static utility methods for HTTP.
      static interface  HttpUtil.METHOD
      The HTTP methods as defined in RFC1945 (HTTP/1.0), RFC2616 (HTTP/1.1), RFC5789 (PATCH) and RFC4918 (WebDAV).
      static class  HttpUtil.STATUS
      The HTTP status codes as defined in RFC1945 (HTTP/1.0), RFC2616 (HTTP/1.1), and RFC4918 (WebDAV).
